name: g2clib
raw_recipe:
package:
    name: g2clib
    version: 1.5.0

source:
    fn: g2clib-1.5.0-patch.tar.gz
    url: http://www.ncl.ucar.edu/Download/files/g2clib-1.5.0-patch.tar.gz
    md5: f857f49a66918316996eb52399e04120

build:
    number: 4
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - libpng 1.6*
        - zlib 1.2*
        - jpeg 9*
        - jasper

test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libgrib2c.a  # [unix]
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test g2clib  # [linux]

about:
    home: http://www.nco.ncep.noaa.gov/pmb/codes/GRIB2/
    license: BSD
    summary: C decoder/encoder routines for GRIB edition 2.

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - jhamman

about.summary: C decoder/encoder routines for GRIB edition 2.
